Class BaseChainedProxyTest

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.littleshoot.proxy.AbstractProxyTest
      • org.littleshoot.proxy.BaseProxyTest
        • org.littleshoot.proxy.BaseChainedProxyTest
  • Direct Known Subclasses:
    BadClientAuthenticationTCPChainedProxyTest, BadServerAuthenticationTCPChainedProxyTest, ClientAuthenticationNotRequiredTCPChainedProxyTest, EncryptedTCPChainedProxyTest, EncryptedUDTChainedProxyTest, MitmWithChainedProxyTest, UnencryptedTCPChainedProxyTest, UnencryptedUDTChainedProxyTest

    public abstract class BaseChainedProxyTest
extends BaseProxyTest
    Base class for tests that test a proxy chained to an upstream proxy. In addition to the usual assertions, this also asserts that every request sent by the downstream proxy was received by the upstream proxy.
